  <description><![CDATA[<p>Experience the wonders of Northern Norway on these great value 3 and 4 night inclusive holidays in <strong>February 2017</strong>, for the perfect combination of pristine snowy scenery with lengthening early spring days and sunshine <strong>now on sale.</strong> All our prices include a whole range of unforgettable activities and experiences amidst this fabulous landscape, including of course the chance to see the spectular <a data-udi="umb://document/280ef861622541caa4a7e53db8f83271" href="/{localLink:umb://document/280ef861622541caa4a7e53db8f83271}" title="Northern Lights">Northern Lights</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Northern Norway is a land of dramatic scenery, whose unique contrast of stunning fjord coastline with mountainous landscapes and snow-covered wilderness inland features an amazing variety of wildlife, both on land and at sea. The locals boast too that this area is located directly under the Aurora Borealis belt, maximising your chances of seeing this phenomenal display, and there’s a special guided evening excursion into the wilderness on your first night to find the best Northern Lights viewing spots.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Based in comfortable hotels in the coastal towns of <a data-udi="umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/229b219729a54801a3d3e6affe22b40b}" title="Narvik - Polar Express Adventure"><strong>Narvik</strong></a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/94fb0f2659f34e2e927f5d59d009f0f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/94fb0f2659f34e2e927f5d59d009f0f4}" title="Vesteralen - Wildlife Adventure"><strong>Vesterålen</strong></a> well above the Arctic Circle, our unique itineraries introduce you to all that this area has to offer, from boat-trips on the fjords to authentic Sami camps with their traditional ‘lavvu’ tents and a choice of snow activities. The ‘Polar Express’ scenic train is another highlight, and there is plenty of local wildlife to see, as well as some unforgettable culinary experiences. With all meals included too (except lunch on arrival &amp; departure day), you’ll also be fully fuelled for your adventure!</p>]]></description>
